	=====================================================================================
	DECADENCE TILEMAPS FILE
	Defines one or more tilemaps for use with the Decadence tile scrolling engine.
	=====================================================================================
	id					The unique resource ID of the tilemap.
	type				The type of the tilemap which is one of "orthogonal",
						"hexagonal" or "isometric". Only orthogonal is supported yet.
	layerCount			How many tile layers the tilemap is comprising of.
	width				The total width of the tilemap, in pixels.
	height				The total height of the tilemap, in pixels.
	=====================================================================================
	mapProperties		These are a list of general properties which are supported
						by a tilemap, e.g. 'backgroundColor' and 'backgroundGradient'
						which affects the background of the whole map or soundID which
						can be used to set a sound ID of a loop that plays while the
